==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Mahdism
<hw>Mah"dism</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Belief in the coming
of the Mahdi; fanatical devotion to the cause of the Mahdi or a
pretender to that title.</def> -- <wordforms><wf>Mah"dist</wf>
<pr>(#)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms></p>

<p><q><qex>Mahdism</qex> has proved the most shameful and terrible
instrument of bloodshed and oppression which the modern world has ever
witnessed.</q> <rj><qau>E. N. Bennett.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Mahican</ent>⟦br⟧
